<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">叠乘法，用因数分解的方法使乘数数位减少或一个乘数的前后段数字互成倍数关系时，能使运算简捷的一种速算方法。可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">mn=m×a+10×(m×a)×b</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中m为被乘数，n为乘数，a为乘数的个位数，n=a+10ab。</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">192×126=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">192×126</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=192×6+10×(192×6)×2</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1152+20×1152</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1152+23040</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=24192</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>